Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下，冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了，來了，戴芬妮來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.68,0:00:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃，快逃，快逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加冕儀式會場上\N出現了基爾特戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方在到處灑落薔薇花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.72,0:00:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輪機室，開到最大航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員進入戰鬥狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它擊沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.13,0:00:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下方有副艦長……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.04,0:00:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個總帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.89,0:01:04.26,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.96,0:01:14.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.17,0:01:22.20,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.28,0:01:28.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.52,0:01:36.45,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.83,0:01:51.14,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.21,0:02:05.64,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.72,0:02:15.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.71,0:02:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}西西里式防禦\NSicilian Defence
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加冕儀式怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也好想看看\N副艦長盛裝的樣子說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.37,0:02:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家可是蘇菲亞皇帝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們船上\N可是坐過個了不得的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說，副艦長可不是蓋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，是花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特為什麼要\N那麼大張旗鼓的來祝賀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.45,0:03:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個天空都被染紅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.82,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是好漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩六天……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問艦長什麼時候才會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.19,0:03:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是和基爾特那位大姐\N曾經有些過節罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦，妳別在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離龍之牙還有800
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接近岩礁中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仰角15度，把高度拉高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細收聽周圍的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.54,0:04:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到有動力音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對照音紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.42,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下方發現了\N無音航行中的烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.72,0:04:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這時候碰到烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是來報仇的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次非得搞定它不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦進入戰鬥位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有皇帝的旗幟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方發出了停戰信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班號要求准許接舷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮總帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還真是打了個大招呼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在讓腦袋冷靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，東西丟得到處都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想讓我擊沈你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝……陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.07,0:05:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照以往那樣\N叫我蘇菲亞就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該在停機庫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.38,0:05:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.06,0:06:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.29,0:06:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是大風暴區的航路圖\N對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.70,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，這是由度西斯所提供的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.57,0:06:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前\N你目擊到EXILE的地點在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.35,0:06:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組件沒有遭到基爾特的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法衝進大風暴區的船艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也只有\N銀之戰艦和烏爾班號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以靠這兩艘來找到EXILE……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要靠銀之戰艦就綽綽有餘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是軍令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有拒絕的權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.88,0:07:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶奪組件行動預定在\N山羊月13日04：00時進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我們必須找到EXILE\N並且抓到它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有……六天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在衝進大風暴區之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由烏爾班號發射音響魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後靠它的搜索音來找出EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.77,0:07:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是光靠搜索音來確認目標\N恐怕……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我才準備了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葳娜\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.24,0:07:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是度西斯所捕捉到的\NEXILE的驅動音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葳娜，妳應該辦得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.62,0:07:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會留在銀之戰艦上擔任指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下\N怎麼可以讓這種破船……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說怎麼可以\N把陛下留在這艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別擔心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對這裡很熟悉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.78,0:08:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那不妙的預感果然應驗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把皇帝旗降下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還挺周到的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝大風暴區出發囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要用用看這架子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很結實唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.37,0:08:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種比賽用的機型\N恐怕抵不住強風吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝……謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長……副艦長她回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是已經是皇帝了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體船員請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:09:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦從現在起將和烏爾班號\N一起朝大風暴區出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大風暴區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.34,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是副艦長的聲音耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本次作戰將與麥德賽艦隊\N以及度西斯殘存艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所組成的同盟艦隊\N採取一致步調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.32,0:09:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來迫使基爾特公會的\N戴芬妮總帥投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將作為主力軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.39,0:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在六天後的山羊月13日04：00前\N找到位於大風暴區中的EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去問問看蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.65,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了在大風暴區裡\N進行聲納搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.12,0:10:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下令無音航行後\N請全艦徹底保持肅靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰是否能夠成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,端看全體船員的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下薪水有著落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.17,0:10:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在此期許各位都能全力以赴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員進入戰鬥位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始朝大風暴區前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.73,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起艦橋工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果妳還是選擇了\N駕駛員這條路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為\N像克勞士那樣的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.68,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有獲准求見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.78,0:11:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.82,0:11:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她到底會怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她和EXILE\N到底有著什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.37,0:11:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒‧薇絲是啟動EXILE\N所不可或缺的一把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是成功搶奪了組件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要對抗基爾特公會\N還是需要EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.95,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE是帶領我們安那托勒\N與度西斯走向和平的最後希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.89,0:12:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對妳而言\N艾兒終究也只是個貨物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護艾兒‧薇絲的安全的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.84,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.65,0:12:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎妳回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨……嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.88,0:13:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些花瓣完全不會枯萎耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.81,0:13:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了對抗基爾特公會\NEXILE是必須的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是蘇菲亞跟你這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，艾兒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫我不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.48,0:13:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就這樣相信了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有夠爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.85,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我會保護艾兒的\N所以不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家好心拿花給他看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.98,0:14:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧他卻……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧他……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒，打起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒妳喜歡蟲子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子？我討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.83,0:14:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我就不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許有人就是討厭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,……生日週？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.81,0:14:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，聽說基爾特的人\N都會慶祝一個禮拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.68,0:14:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是生日應該是一件\N值得高興的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.02,0:14:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果沒有人幫忙慶祝\N是很寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.27,0:15:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼纜不夠長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，莫藍你拿鋼纜給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.80,0:15:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍走了以後\N你好像滿寂寞的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他如果繼續待在這裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以成為一個\N技術高超的維修士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經找到自己要走的路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到迪奧嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無能可是一種罪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.64,0:15:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是在把水運往乾旱的地帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.11,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真難看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它的組件收回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.25,0:15:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他們並沒有違反任何規則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就照您的意思去辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.46,0:16:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯的船\N馬上就會把水運過來了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.90,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荷莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這就要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次什麼時候回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.41,0:16:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會有一場大戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.12,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那位總帥\N給同盟的回答嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一切結束後\N我立刻就會來接妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.84,0:17:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是度西斯的最新型嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡栓得太緊了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.31,0:17:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會比較好用哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你胸口那個是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.63,0:17:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.46,0:17:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我活著回來的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數目好多哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.23,0:17:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勸妳最好不要離開我身邊哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.31,0:18:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我又提前出局了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟拉薇，還有塔琪安娜的時候\N也都是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又是鳥肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是鳥蛋你都吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳥蛋和鳥不一樣好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.03,0:18:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不吃鳥肉的話\N當心沒有體力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是克勞士\N也能和我們一起飛就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子乘著銀之戰艦\N飛到很高的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼跩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得他是去幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是去殺無赦去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們都進步很快嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.53,0:18:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了我可是拿到\N諾齊亞盃冠軍的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我住嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是狗屎運撈到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式行動時也拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.75,0:19:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是宣誓的印記嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你將會失去\N飛翔在天空的自由與快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣你也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼所謂無所謂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這是戴芬妮決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也只有這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉……真是令人討厭的儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.77,0:19:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想永遠都待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.22,0:19:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砂糖好像加得太多了點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.82,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做出來才好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.62,0:19:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是……是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越來越接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看看好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到外頭去看大風暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是度西斯船艦殘骸的反射音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.78,0:20:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是雨候鳥拍翅的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.02,0:20:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最初的第一發……在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.39,0:20:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於要衝入大風暴區了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離捕獲EXILE的最後期限\N還剩五天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.36,0:20:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射魚雷的這一方\N責任也相當重大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.77,0:20:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音響魚雷，準備發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班號來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魚雷發射已準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別走得太遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷……好冰的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.04,0:21:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入大風暴區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作好衝擊防備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.88,0:21:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦準備進行無音航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.19,0:21:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關閉所有隔艙，停止空調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.66,0:21:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會還是\N不要用堆起來的比較好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.03,0:21:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保……保持安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽音準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.51,0:22:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，發射音響魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.42,0:22:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是\N吞噬了爸爸他們的大風暴區……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.38,0:22:39.61,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.25,0:22:46.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.26,0:22:51.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.53,0:22:57.30,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.37,0:23:03.04,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.11,0:23:11.88,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.95,0:23:17.75,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
